commit.title: Simplify and fix the libobject of Argument Scopes
commit.message:
Simplify and fix the libobject of Argument Scopes

We do not change the semantics, except for a few bugs when the scope
cache was not recomputed. In particular, we keep the dynamic binding
effect `Bind Scope` has on argument scopes.
